            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>LucaNet receives ISO 27001 certification</h3><div><p>LucaNet Cloud Services GmbH, a wholly owned subsidiary of LucaNet AG, has successfully passed the certification audit for information security management systems (ISMS) according to ISO/IEC 27001, ISO 27001 for short, and has thus taken a further step towards sustainable security processes.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/lucanet-receives-iso-27001-certification/" title="">Read more</a></div></div>
            <div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate">
              <div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">09.01.</div><div class="year">2020</div></div>
            </div>
           <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>Certent and LucaNet Partner to Streamline the Financial Close and Report Production Process</h3><div><p>LucaNet, provider of financial performance management software, today announced a partnership with Certent, Inc., a leading provider of software-as-a-service solutions for financial disclosure management and equity compensation.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/certent-and-lucanet-partner-to-streamline-the-financial-close-and-report-production-process/" title="">Read more</a></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="row articleline"><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">02.10.</div><div class="year">2019</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>On course for further success: LucaNet strong in the first half of 2019</h3><div><p>After a 14 percent increase in revenue in 2018, LucaNet, an expert in Financial Performance Management, is well on its way to outperforming this result in 2019. The Berlin-based company remains on its growth trajectory and increased its sales in the first half of 2019 by 30 percent compared to the same period last year. New customer business is also going according to plan: 153 new customers opted for LucaNet's software solutions in the first half of 2019.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/on-course-for-further-success-lucanet-strong-in-the-first-half-of-2019/" title="">Read more</a></div></div><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">19.11.</div><div class="year">2018</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>Simply fast – LucaNet migrates to Java 11</h3><div><p>With its new LucaNet 11 LTS release, LucaNet, provider of financial performance management software, has carried off the migration from Java 8 to Java 11 at lightning speed. In connection with the conversion, the Berlin-based software firm has developed the so-called LucaNet.Software Manager, which kick-starts LucaNet programs with ease and keeps them up-to-date. The current release also includes numerous new functions and enhancements that make daily work that much easier.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/simply-fast-lucanet-migrates-to-java-11/" title="">Read more</a></div></div></div>
          <div class="row articleline"><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">05.09.</div><div class="year">2018</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>Vamos a España – LucaNet opens new site in Madrid</h3><div><p>LucaNet, provider of financial performance management, continues to grow. September 1, 2018 heralds the arrival of another new member of the LucaNet family, on Madrid's famous Paseo de la Castellana. The opening of the Spanish site brings the total number of countries in which LucaNet is represented to 11. Madrid native Pedro Mardomingo will be in charge of business activities in Spain.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/vamos-a-espana-lucanet-opens-new-site-in-madrid/" title="">Read more</a></div></div><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">02.07.</div><div class="year">2018</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>LucaNet crowned TOP CONSULTANT once again</h3><div><p>The number of consulting companies in their various incarnations continues to increase. But only very few companies are allowed to carry the sought-after TOP CONSULTANT seal for best consultant for medium-sized enterprises. On June 29, 2018, LucaNet, this year also, joined the ranks of the best for a fourth time in the category of management consulting, as awarded by mentor Christian Wulff.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/lucanet-crowned-top-consultant-once-again/" title="">Read more</a></div></div></div>
          <div class="row articleline"><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">24.04.</div><div class="year">2018</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>LucaNet grows by 38%</h3><div><p>LucaNet, a provider of software and consulting services for financial performance management, continued to enjoy rapid growth in the 2017 financial year. Having already recorded a 27% increase in sales in 2016, the LucaNet Group managed to surpass that result last year to the tune of 38%. Meanwhile, the 350 customers it gained in 2017 include prominent names such as Avira, Ernst &amp; Young, and Wilco Farmers.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/lucanet-grows-by-38/" title="">Read more</a></div></div><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">10.04.</div><div class="year">2018</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>Simply the best – LucaNet rated market leader in BARC Score for Financial Performance Management</h3><div><p>LucaNet, the expert in financial performance management (FPM), has prevailed as a market leader for financial performance management solutions in the latest study from BARC. In the study, LucaNet stood out thanks to its very good market positioning and its comprehensive software suite. The suite covers all relevant processes in a finance department.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/simply-the-best-lucanet-rated-market-leader-in-barc-score-for-financial-performance-management/" title="">Read more</a></div></div></div>
          <div class="row articleline"><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">22.03.</div><div class="year">2018</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>Fast Track to Success: SEG Automotive Switches to LucaNet for Consolidated Financial Statements</h3><div><p>Former division of Bosch using LucaNet software for consolidation, planning, and reporting:&nbsp;SEG Automotive Germany GmbH will be entrusting its consolidated financial statements to LucaNet from now on. Established as an independent company in early 2018, Bosch's former starter motors and generators division – which employs over 8,000 people at 16 locations around the world – is now using LucaNet software to optimize its financial processes.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/fast-track-to-success-seg-automotive-switches-to-lucanet-for-consolidated-financial-statements/" title="">Read more</a></div></div><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">13.10.</div><div class="year">2017</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>New Lünendonk study</h3><div><p>Market for business intelligence and business analytics continues to grow – LucaNet heads up list of most successful enterprises based in Germany</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/new-lunendonk-study/" title="">Read more</a></div></div></div>
          <div class="row articleline"><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">10.05.</div><div class="year">2017</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>LucaNet further expands its business in the U.S.</h3><div><p>The German corporate performance management software provider LucaNet is stepping up its North American activities by opening its own subsidiary in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania. Situated in the heart of the city, the office serves as a hub for all the company's business in the U.S. and Canada. Help will now be close at hand for the American companies previously served from Germany.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/lucanet-further-expands-its-business-in-the-u-s/" title="">Read more</a></div></div><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">06.04.</div><div class="year">2017</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>LucaNet expands business relationship in the Middle East</h3><div><p>LucaNet, provider of software and consulting services for corporate performance management, has entered into a sales partnership for the Middle East with Foresee Solutions. The Berlin enterprise is setting its foot in the MENA region for the first time.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/lucanet-expands-business-relationship-in-the-middle-east/" title="">Read more</a></div></div></div>
          <div class="row articleline"><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">30.03.</div><div class="year">2017</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>LucaNet continues on the road to success – a strong year in 2016</h3><div><ul><li>Sales up 27%</li><li>270 new customers worldwide</li><li>New offices in Singapore and the USA</li></ul><p>LucaNet, provider of software and consulting services for corporate performance management, continued to enjoy rapid growth in the 2016 financial year. The company generated another double-digit increase in sales, this time of an impressive 27%. With the opening of its own offices in Singapore and the USA, LucaNet remains focused on its plans for internationalisation and now boasts thirteen sites in nine countries.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/lucanet-continues-on-the-road-to-success-a-strong-year-in-2016/" title="">Read more</a></div></div><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">16.03.</div><div class="year">2017</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>LucaNet and Sage – smooth integration thanks to their technological partnership</h3><div><p>LucaNet, the provider of software and consulting services for Corporate Performance Management, and Sage GmbH, one of the leading enterprise solution providers, have entered into a comprehensive technological partnership. The partnership initially applies to Sage X3, the global ERP solution for midcaps, but should be quickly expanded to include other systems. Linking the two systems offers users a high-performance ERP system supplemented by the diverse options of LucaNet in the areas of analysis, reporting, planning and consolidated financial statements.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/lucanet-and-sage-smooth-integration-thanks-to-their-technological-partnership/" title="">Read more</a></div></div></div>
          <div class="row articleline"><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">09.03.</div><div class="year">2017</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>LucaNet 10 optimises financial controlling</h3><div><p>LucaNet sets new market standards</p><p>LucaNet AG, provider of software and consulting services for Financial Corporate Performance Management, has released a new version of its software for consolidation, planning, reporting and analysis. With LucaNet 10, the Berlin-based enterprise is launching an automated system that optimises all financial controlling processes and provides finance managers with all the information they need to make their decisions, more quickly and accurately than ever before. The release will introduce an array of new features to increase the efficiency of financial processes.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/lucanet-10-optimises-financial-controlling/" title="">Read more</a></div></div><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">22.11.</div><div class="year">2016</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>LucaNet opens ASEAN Region Office in Singapore</h3><div><p>LucaNet AG, Europe’s leading provider of integrated Financial Corporate Performance Management solutions (FCPM), has opened an office in Singapore. The new site will be the headquarters for the complete ASEAN region.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/lucanet-opens-asean-region-office-in-singapore/" title="">Read more</a></div></div></div>
          <div class="row articleline"><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">11.10.</div><div class="year">2016</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>New Lünendonk study: German market for business intelligence and business analytics continues to grow – LucaNet reaches 2nd place among enterprises based in Germany</h3><div><p>LucaNet AG, provider of software and consulting services for business intelligence in the field of accounting, has been ranked the seventh-biggest software manufacturer for business intelligence and business analytics solutions in the latest Lünendonk study, entitled "The market for business intelligence and business analytics in Germany". With a turnover of 13.5 million euros in Germany, the Berlin-based enterprise was able to improve its ranking by five places compared to the previous year. The first five places were taken by subsidiaries of the big American BI specialists.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/new-lunendonk-study-german-market-for-business-intelligence-and-business-analytics-continues-to-grow-lucanet-reaches-2nd-place-among-enterprises-based-in-germany/" title="">Read more</a></div></div><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">04.05.</div><div class="year">2016</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>Serviceplan to use LucaNet software for its consolidation</h3><div><p>To prepare its consolidated financial statements, the international communications agency Serviceplan will soon be using products from LucaNet, the provider of software and consulting services for business intelligence in accounting. The move is the company's response to its strong growth at group level and the increased demands that this makes of group accounting.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/serviceplan-to-use-lucanet-software-for-its-consolidation/" title="">Read more</a></div></div></div>
          <div class="row articleline"><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">25.04.</div><div class="year">2016</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>LucaNet and proALPHA to partner on technology</h3><div><p>LucaNet AG, the provider of software and consulting services for business intelligence in accounting, has entered into a comprehensive technological partnership with the ERP provider proALPHA. Combining the two systems will allow users to marry proALPHA's powerful ERP solution with the varied possibilities that LucaNet offers for consolidation, planning, reporting and analysis.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/lucanet-and-proalpha-to-partner-on-technology/" title="">Read more</a></div></div><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">16.03.</div><div class="year">2016</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>LucaNet continues on the road to success – a strong year in 2015</h3><div><p>LucaNet AG, the provider of software and consulting services for consolidation, planning, reporting and analysis, has published its sales figures for 2015. With growth of 30 %, the Berlin-based enterprise has once again exceeded expectations.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/lucanet-continues-on-the-road-to-success-a-strong-year-in-2015/" title="">Read more</a></div></div></div>
          <div class="row articleline"><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">08.03.</div><div class="year">2016</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>LucaNet AG and AMANA consulting GmbH seal technological partnership</h3><div><p>LucaNet AG has entered into a new technological partnership with AMANA consulting GmbH. Amana's "SmartNotes" disclosure management tool is the perfect addition to the portfolio of products offered by LucaNet as a specialist in software for business intelligence in accounting.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/lucanet-ag-and-amana-consulting-gmbh-seal-technological-partnership/" title="">Read more</a></div></div><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">06.11.</div><div class="year">2015</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>LucaNet UK Limited Announce Their First Premium UK Partner, HAYNE Solutions Limited)</h3><div><p>LucaNet UK Limited is today delighted to announce their first Premium partner here in the UK, HAYNE Solutions Limited.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/lucanet-uk-limited-announce-their-first-premium-uk-partner-hayne-solutions-limited/" title="">Read more</a></div></div></div>
          <div class="row articleline"><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">15.09.</div><div class="year">2015</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>LucaNet reports 19% more turnover in the first half year</h3><div><p>LucaNet AG, software and consultation provider for business intelligence in accounting, has had a successful start to 2015. The enterprise recorded a turnover increase of 19% in the first six months. The number of new customers also matches the figures from the previous year.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/lucanet-reports-19-more-turnover-in-the-first-half-year/" title="">Read more</a></div></div><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">10.09.</div><div class="year">2015</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>LucaNet gains successful foothold in Great Britain</h3><div><p>LucaNet AG, software and consultation provider for business intelligence in accounting, has now been officially represented with a company in Great Britain since September 2015. In addition to its offices near London, LucaNet is also represented through a sales partnership with LSA Solutions. Initial clients come from the information technology and tourism branches.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/lucanet-gains-successful-foothold-in-great-britain/" title="">Read more</a></div></div></div>
          <div class="row articleline"><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">29.06.</div><div class="year">2015</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>LucaNet makes "Top Consultant" again</h3><div><p>Berlin: LucaNet AG, provider of software and consulting services for BI in the field of accounting, has again won the compamedia "Top Consultant" seal of quality. This is the third time the Berlin-based company has received the award for its qualities as a management consultancy provider. As mentor to the consultant comparison association, former German Federal President Christian Wulff presented LucaNet with the award at the German Summit for Medium-Sized Companies on 26 June in Essen.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/lucanet-makes-top-consultant-again/" title="">Read more</a></div></div><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">18.02.</div><div class="year">2015</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>27% more: LucaNet manages to increase its sales again and looks back on a successful year 2014</h3><div><ul><li>Sales increase by 27%</li><li>Number of staff goes up 12%</li><li>180 new customers</li><li>New subsidiary in Switzerland</li></ul><p>Berlin-based LucaNet AG looks back on a successful 2014 financial year. The specialist for business intelligence in accounting managed to increase its sales again by double figures. The 180 new customers acquired contributed significantly to this.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/27-more-lucanet-manages-to-increase-its-sales-again-and-looks-back-on-a-successful-year-2014/" title="">Read more</a></div></div></div>
          <div class="row articleline"><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">13.02.</div><div class="year">2015</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>LucaNet now also in France</h3><div><ul><li>LucaNet opens offices in Paris</li><li>Stéphane Pimienta is the Managing Director of LucaNet France</li><li>Demand among French companies for powerful solutions like LucaNet is high</li></ul><ul></ul><p>LucaNet AG, a specialist for business intelligence in accounting, drives development on at an international level. By opening a subsidiary in Paris, LucaNet is boosting its presence on the French market while also expanding its range of products and services.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/lucanet-now-also-in-france/" title="">Read more</a></div></div><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">25.11.</div><div class="year">2014</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>Successful LucaNet user convention in Berlin</h3><div><p>Top-quality presentations and an interested audience of experts – the LucaNet user convention, held at the Steigenberger Hotel in Berlin, was a complete success.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/successful-lucanet-user-convention-in-berlin/" title="">Read more</a></div></div></div>
          <div class="row articleline"><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">19.11.</div><div class="year">2014</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>Partnership cubed: arcplan and LucaNet pool their expertise in planning, consolidation and analysis</h3><div><p>The business intelligence expert and consolidation specialist decided to form a strategic partnership. This gives customers a uniform system for planning, budgeting, consolidation, right up to reporting and analysis.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/partnership-cubed-arcplan-and-lucanet-pool-their-expertise-in-planning-consolidation-and-analysis/" title="">Read more</a></div></div><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">07.10.</div><div class="year">2014</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>LucaNet AG awarded "TOP CONSULTANT" 2014/2015</h3><div><p>Berlin-based LucaNet AG is one of the 100 best medium-sized consulting companies in Germany – Top Consultant seal awarded for fifth time</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/lucanet-ag-awarded-top-consultant-2014-2015/" title="">Read more</a></div></div></div>
          <div class="row articleline"><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">26.08.</div><div class="year">2014</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>Strong first half in 2014: Sales up 22%</h3><div><p>Berlin-based software provider and consultancy LucaNet AG, a specialist in consolidation, planning, reporting and analysis, recorded a 22% year-on-year rise in sales for the first six months of the year, and acquired some prominent customers.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/strong-first-half-in-2014-sales-up-22/" title="">Read more</a></div></div><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">14.04.</div><div class="year">2014</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>Businesses are not prepared for Management reporting of the future</h3><div><ul><li>Organisational structures and staff shortages are standing in the way of modern management reporting</li><li>Role of CFO continues to grow in importance</li><li>LucaNet and Lünendonk present new theories about the future of management reporting</li><li>Study now available for <a href="https://www.lucanet.com/en/info-center/whitepaper/3-x-3-bi-the-future-of-management-reporting/"> free download </a></li></ul><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/businesses-are-not-prepared-for-management-reporting-of-the-future/" title="">Read more</a></div></div></div>
          <div class="row articleline"><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">28.01.</div><div class="year">2014</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>LucaNet – 15 years' worth of expertise in the accounting field</h3><div><p>The Berlin-based company LucaNet AG is celebrating its 15th anniversary this year. Over the last five years alone, the successful specialist for business intelligence has grown by 162%.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/lucanet-15-years-worth-of-expertise-in-the-accounting-field/" title="">Read more</a></div></div><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">11.11.</div><div class="year">2013</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>LucaNet AG presented with the Technology Fast 50 Award</h3><div><p>The Berlin-based company LucaNet AG has grown by over 162 per cent over the last five years. This puts the specialist for business intelligence in accounting among the 50 fastest growing technology companies in Germany.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/lucanet-ag-presented-with-the-technology-fast-50-award/" title="">Read more</a></div></div></div>
          <div class="row articleline"><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">16.07.</div><div class="year">2013</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>LucaNet among top ten providers of BI software</h3><div><p>In the latest BARC study on the 2012 business intelligence software market, LucaNet makes it into the top ten largest German providers with a sales growth of 39%.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/lucanet-among-top-ten-providers-of-bi-software/" title="">Read more</a></div></div><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">20.06.</div><div class="year">2013</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>LucaNet picks up top marks in customer survey</h3><div><p>The Berlin-based company LucaNet AG, provider of software and consulting services for consolidation, planning, reporting and analysis, achieved great results in a recently conducted customer satisfaction survey. The company performed extremely well in the areas of software, support and consultant expertise in particular.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/lucanet-picks-up-top-marks-in-customer-survey/" title="">Read more</a></div></div></div>
          <div class="row articleline"><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">21.01.</div><div class="year">2013</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>40% more sales: in 2012 LucaNet tops its result from the previous year</h3><div><p>The Berlin-based company LucaNet AG, provider of software and consulting services for consolidation, planning, reporting and analysis, has once again recorded an enormous growth in sales with an increase of 40% in 2012. Over 150 newly acquired customers in particular contributed to this development.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/40-more-sales-in-2012-lucanet-tops-its-result-from-the-previous-year/" title="">Read more</a></div></div><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">03.09.</div><div class="year">2012</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>Simply intelligent - LucaNet 9.0 includes new modules for fast and reliable accounting processes</h3><div><p>LucaNet AG, a leading provider of software for consolidation, planning, reporting and analysis, presented the Release of 9.0. This year the focus is primarily on the newly designed and expanded product portfolio.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/simply-intelligent-lucanet-9-0-includes-new-modules-for-fast-and-reliable-accounting-processes/" title="">Read more</a></div></div></div>
          <div class="row articleline"><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">17.07.</div><div class="year">2012</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>Over 40% more turnover: First half of 2012 a total success for LucaNet</h3><div><p>After a very successful year in 2011, the Berlin LucaNet AG built on these positive developments in the first half of 2012. With revenue growth of over 40% compared to the same period last year and an increase in orders received, the company is confident of exceeding its own targets again in 2012, thus reinforcing its claim to the innovation and market leadership for integrated software solutions in the area of consolidation, planning, reporting and analysis. Among the previously more than 70 new customers, there are companies such as Westfleisch eG, STIEBEL ELTRON GmbH &amp; Co. KG, Hapag-Lloyd Kreuzfahrten GmbH and the Wiener Börse AG.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/over-40-more-turnover-first-half-of-2012-a-total-success-for-lucanet/" title="">Read more</a></div></div><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">12.03.</div><div class="year">2012</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>LucaNet awarded with IT Innovation Prize 2012</h3><div><p>The ceremony to award the Innovation Prize 2012 was held last Friday at the CeBIT, the trade fair showcasing digital IT &amp; telecommunications solutions. The winners include the Berlin software manufacturer, LucaNet. The solutions for consolidation, planning, reporting and analysis convinced the jury with their high utility value, their innovativeness and their suitability for small and medium sized enterprises.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/lucanet-awarded-with-it-innovation-prize-2012/" title="">Read more</a></div></div></div>
          <div class="row articleline"><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">20.07.</div><div class="year">2011</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>Leica consolidates with LucaNet</h3><div><p>Leica Camera AG has introduced the LucaNet.World software solution for its legal consolidation and corporate management. In future, the tool by the Berlin-based software producer will automatically perform the monthly consolidation.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/leica-consolidates-with-lucanet/" title="">Read more</a></div></div><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">14.04.</div><div class="year">2011</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>LucaNet strengthens its presence in the Benelux countries</h3><div><p>LucaNet is entering the Belgian market: on 1 March 2011 a new subsidiary opened. Strategically located in Mortsel, close to Antwerp in the heart of Flanders, LucaNet firstly aims to penetrate the Belgian market by attaining a solid client base in the Flemish region before expanding its sales activities into the Walloon region.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/lucanet-strengthens-its-presence-in-the-benelux-countries/" title="">Read more</a></div></div></div>
          <div class="row articleline"><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">11.08.</div><div class="year">2010</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>LucaNet launches software for capital participations onto the market</h3><div><p>Under the name LucaNet.<strong>Equity</strong>, the company LucaNet AG, leading provider of software, seminars and consultancy for business intelligence in accounting, is offering a software for capital participations.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/lucanet-launches-software-for-capital-participations-onto-the-market/" title="">Read more</a></div></div><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">20.04.</div><div class="year">2010</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>LucaNet starts operations in Shanghai</h3><div><p>Using the name Lan Ke, the Berlin software producer LucaNet is expanding into the Far East. From its base in Shanghai, the aim is to conquer the Chinese market. The software for this purpose has already been translated into Chinese and is available for sale starting now.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/lucanet-starts-operations-in-shanghai/" title="">Read more</a></div></div></div>
          <div class="row articleline"><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">11.05.</div><div class="year">2009</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>LucaNet.Financial Intelligence Suite officially tested</h3><div><p>LucaNet, the leading provider for business intelligence in accounting, has received an unrestricted endorsement of the quality and regularity of its software. Thus it is confirmed to the Berlin company that the LucaNet.Financial Intelligence Suite corresponds to all the rules of proper accounting.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/lucanet-financial-intelligence-suite-officially-tested/" title="">Read more</a></div></div><div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 articleDate"><div class="articleDate-inner"><div class="day">25.02.</div><div class="year">2009</div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-10 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 articleContent"><h3>The first specialist OLAP Database worldwide for BI in accounting</h3><div><p>At CeBIT 2009 (Hall 4, Stand A66) LucaNet - leading provider of software, seminars and consultancy for financial intelligence – is presenting the first specialist database for Real-Time Financial OLAP. For the first time, all calculations and analyses can be made in real time.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/info-center/press-releases/the-first-specialist-olap-database-worldwide-for-bi-in-accounting/" title="">Read more</a></div></div></div>
